{
  "stem": "26983.12",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "DP camps years.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or they had at once to struggle and care for themselves and get the ration cards and food, et cetera, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the world after liberation in '45.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we arrived there in the middle of-- or the end of June-- the middle-- I think the end of June.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And slowly, we-- through the better food and enormously human and lovely care--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He had, of course, a staff of people who helped him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a kind of represent of the Ministry of Social Welfare, and therefore, he had a free hand to go, after the war, to all the camps and take the most needed children-- not only Jewish but Czech and German children who were, at that time, also in camps-- and bring them over.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in this way, he helped us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I've been in contact with him all these years, till he died, in-- I think in '74 or so.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we children managed, also, that he got a medal of the Jewish State and the tree--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--in Yad Vashem for the Righteous One of the non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he's a righteous--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
